<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Aw Thisan Lul!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Suih lunghel in ginnan vak thil leu hang,
 A lang van gam lopi;
 Lei a lungngai chate tuol a lennau,
 Belam No leh Hinna Thing pak tanin;
 Hehpihte a leng ui,
 A lopi ie kipakin la sai tiu.

[V2]
 Aw, thisan lul zaila'n hun chawian ka,
 Nei hehpihna lopi;
 Kalvaria tatna thisan,
 Zaila'n chawian ingka.

[V3]
 2. Suihlung helin, thil bang cheng gelviel leng,
 Kipahna a hung nai;
 Hehpihpa thisan zala kipahna,
 I vang nei ngei Pathien chate hi din;
 Krista'n ei na siem tai,
 Kipahna kim nasepna hi ahi.

[V4]
 3. Ka chantawk a kipahna lopi pen,
 Hehpih thiengtho ahi;
 Pathien cha leh A nasem hihna tawh,
 Ei veng bitin keimah ahin semin;
 Aw ka Lalpa deihtak,
 Ei mangin aw thagau hukdam dingin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>94</hymn_number>
</song>